238
00:11:41,367 --> 00:11:42,761
- Wait, wait, wait
- I like it!

239
00:11:42,867 --> 00:11:44,824
- That’s gonna be easy to market!
- Yes!

240
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,200
We can do it, Mom.

241
00:11:46,225 --> 00:11:49,325
Wait a minute,
we need to tell your Daddy about this.

242
00:11:50,325 --> 00:11:54,510
Of course we will,
but first we need to make sure that

243
00:11:54,534 --> 00:11:58,743
